data.description:
Back on the market. Preserve home lot in North Creek. Great location to shopping, 295 and 95. Newer roof, Spacious downstairs with formal living, dinning and a flex room/office with doors that would be converted into a 6th bedroom. Financing fell through. New Carpet, new paint, new kitchen backsplash downstairs.  
All bedrooms upstairs. Vaulted ceilings.
